name: DSQUARED SHE VELVET FOREST 50ML

name: DSQUARED HE ROCKY MOUNTAIN 100ML
campo_tres: La fragancia está inspirada en las montañas de Canadá y, como su nombre indica, está diseñado y dedicado a los amantes de la naturaleza. Se compone de notas rocosas, los aromas de montaña y acuerdos de madera y notas como el ámbar,incienso y almizcle, que reflejan las notas rocosas, junto con violeta, lirio de Canadá y pimienta blanca. Vetiver y cedro terminan la composición.
campo_seis: Dsquared2 He Wood Rocky Mountain Wood is a new fragrance for men by the house of Dsquared2. It belongs to collection Dsquared2 Nature Always Wins, which is different, unique and complementary to other fragrances, as well as connected directly with theme of the house of Dsquared2. Fragrance Dsquared2 He Wood Rocky Mountain Wood was inspired by Canadian mountains and, as its name suggests, it is designed and dedicated to fans of nature. It is composed of rocky notes, mountain aromas and woody accords. The fragrance was reated by Daphne Bugey, of such notes as amber, incense and musk, which reflect rocky notes, along with violet, Canadian lily and white pepper. Vetiver and cedar finish the composition.

name: DSQUARED POTION EDP 50ML
campo_tres: Los diseñadores Dean y Dan Caten o Dsquared2, ofrecen este nuevo perfume inspirado en una alquimia mágica que evoca todos los deseos carnales y la lujuria- constituyendo toda una herramienta de seducción y conquista. La composición es leñosa con notas de fondo de ámbar, desarrollada por Annick Menardo. Siendo como antes les adelantábamos una receta de seducción olfativa y una poción lograda mediante ingredientes de calidad para despertar los deseos amorosos
campo_seis: DSquared2 Potion is the second men's fragrance -not counting the limited editions- of the Canadian designer duo Dean and Dan Caten or DSquared2. In collaboration with the Italian company ITF, they launched their first men's fragrance He Wood in 2007, followed by the female version She Wood in 2008. The new fragrance is named Potion. It represents a tool of seduction, conquer and emotions and is inspired by the chemical workshops of the past. Potion is designed as a magical alchemy that evokes carnal desires and lust. The composition is aromatic woody with a distinctive background of amber. It is developed by Annick Menard. A new recipe of olfactory seduction and a potion of quality ingredients arousing amorous desires is made of- Top notes red mint leaves, angelica and thyme. Heart rose petals, black peppercorns, tear drops of gentian and cinnamon sticks. Base- cashmere wood, patchouli, amber and musk

name: GAFAS ITALIA INDEPENDENT
campo_tres: These are the 090V glasses, the most outstanding model of the 2010-11 I-wear collection, reviewing an iconic shape of the Italian eyewear tradition and proposing a velvet effect. Italia Independent is the first company in the eyewear industry that has introduced the velvet-effect in its range of eyewear processing methods. The surface of glasses is soft to the touch as if they were coated with velvet. Apart from providing glasses with a special material quality, this treatment is scratch-proof.

name: RELOJ V-RACE CHRONO BLK DIAL
campo_seis: V-Race has a sporty style with a positive and forceful personality on account of its unique detailing. The round 42mm case in steel features interchangeable lunettes. This chronograph version with a retrograde seconds function underlines the all-action character of the V-Race. The case in IP-coated rose gold frames a the dial on which the Medusa and Versace logos are clearly visible at 12 o’clock. The three counters express the dynamic quality of this watch with its Swiss ETA G15.26 1 movement. To complement this superb timepiece, the attractive black strap comes in alligator-print leather with butterfly fastening. name: CDG2 MAN 100ML
campo_tres: COMME DES GARCONS - MAN 2 - 50 ML SPRAY - The fragrance that's causing crazed mobs to empty the shelves in Europe and Japan is here! CdG 2 MAN is a revision of the original 2 (in the silver bottle), taking it in a more woody/incense direction and creating a whole new animal. Smoldering at first, 2 MAN roars out of the gate, declaring its boldness and contempt for simpering little focus-group scents that are a mishmash of manly notes. 2 MAN's simmering and incensey opening unfolds into an unusual combination of nutmeg, vetiver and subtle saffron flowers, each one appearing like chapters in a book. As the pages turn and it evolves on the skin, a subdued mahogany and leather bring up the rear. Daring but not brash or loud. complex yet never persnickety. It's a sure-bet for a modern classic.

name: DSQUARED HE WOOD EDT VP 50ML
campo_tres: He Wood, un perfume masculino amaderado vetiver creado por la multinacional Firmenich. Agua, aire y madera, tres elementos primitivos que desnudan la naturaleza como un lujo escaso, tierno y seductor. Más madera en el fondo del perfume con notas predominantes de madera de cedro y raíces de vetiver, seducción y tranquilidad.
campo_seis: He Wood by DSQUARED2 is a Woody Aromatic fragrance for men. He Wood was launched in 2007. The nose behind this fragrance is Daphne Bugey. Top notes are violet and violet leaf. middle notes are vetiver and cedar, base notes are amber, musk and fir.

name: PERFUME EXPLORER 50ML
campo_tres: This is citrus gone over to the dark side. The bitter notes of lemon and citron, intensified by the camphoraceous, piney facets of cypress, give way to the deep purple duet of orris and violet. But there’s nothing powdery and nostalgic about this interlude- the orris is stately, the violet a mere touch of sweetness. Clad in smooth leather, bathed in the warm honeyed fumes of tobacco leaves, Explorer forges on its path towards he secret realm of oud, and settles in its pitch-black, medicinal aroma. He’ll never make it back to the Royal Geographical Society to report his findings. Neither will you.

campo_tres: This is citrus gone over to the dark side. The bitter notes of lemon and citron, intensified by the camphoraceous, piney facets of cypress, give way to the deep purple duet of orris and violet. But there’s nothing powdery and nostalgic about this interlude- the orris is stately, the violet a mere touch of sweetness. Clad in smooth leather, bathed in the warm honeyed fumes of tobacco leaves, Explorer forges on its path towards he secret realm of oud, and settles in its pitch-black, medicinal aroma. He’ll never make it back to the Royal Geographical Society to report his findings. Neither will you.

name: PERFUME INTENSE 50ML
campo_tres: We were momentarily taken aback by the name after our first sniff. Intense? Intensely cozy, maybe. Boadicea’s quixotic take on a fruity floral has a powdery, enveloping sweetness that puts it in the same league as some of our favorite grown-up comfort scents. A light crisp citrus leads us to a sweet bouquet of blossoms loaded with pollen – velvety lily, plummy rose and delicate jasmine – nestled in a soft, pillowy cloud of vanilla and patchouli. Delectable and exotic, this has the dreamy edible flower quality of confections like rosewater ice cream and Turkish Delight. In spite of its softness, this has an insistent quality - like someone whispering in your ear. You want to lean in for another sniff – to decipher the enigmatic muskiness of the vanilla, to experience the unexpected freshness of the lily. Deliciously seductive.

name: PERFUME COMPLEX 50ML
campo_tres: The mood is Gothic- the scene, a dungeon- the scent, an unsettling dip into olfactory taboos. This is leather at its darkest, spiked with metallic studs of violet, lashed with the aromatic essences of basil and sage. Cistus labdanum straddles the boundary between the herbal and animal realms, before submitting to the whip of leather – tarry, bitter, almost licorice-like in its somber facets. An animal aroma of civet and musk suffuses the scene with the smell of hot, yielding flesh. Incense fumes bathe the ritual in their searing whorls. Heed the stern command of Complex and let the ceremony commence. Just don’t say you haven’t been warned.

name: PERFUME REGAL 50ML
campo_tres: Very fleeting green leafy notes at first, then lots of warm floral jasmine and rose with amber. As it warms on my skin I get more rose than jasmine, and the agarwood becomes more apparent with a slight tobacco-y note to the warm woody base.  This is definitely an evening fragrance for me, and not an office one- it has serious throw and lasts all day. This is a more feminine fragrance to my nose.
